{"tid":808674,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港整個大型老人城點睇","createTime":"2018-09-06T13:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T07:28:25.000Z","uid":197959,"like":91,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1f71315010794e83a6149aeae0aef19dd8cc2bf5","tid":808674,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"可能有啲極端<br />\n<br />\n平時有時去醫院都見到超多老人家,香港人咁長壽都係因為醫院太近,老人家有事冇事都睇,所以一直死唔去,因為咁人口老化越黎越嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老人城就好似外國啲大型老人院咁,位置就係啲郊區發展,有晒娛樂,運動,公園之類嘅野,佢地鍾意點鳩叫都冇人受影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老嘅係埋一齊只可以自己打自己人,又唔怕咩獨居老人,又可以算係退休計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面仲可以控制佢地嘅生死,冇人可以check到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半強制性<br />\n如果唔想入去就要証明係社會嘅有一定貢獻值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣廢老霸住嘅公屋就要比晒出黎,公共褔利攞極都有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真有錢人緊係可以有方法唔去<br />\n但係海外有資產但扮窮嘅就死撚晒,一定會驚到走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實外國啲老人家老咗都自己識死去老人院,係得華人社會先鍾意咁搞9啲後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf297328ffbc4b776b46212b0a40a47030912d5","tid":808674,"uid":197959,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0825ac124a27b65bf4727065eb8f1e9056561c05","tid":808674,"uid":207426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f51cef43ef1835b835bc03d33e72b6c0172a0b0","tid":808674,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣已經係"},{"pid":"3eada5bfb85e774f99ffd7781dd02694adb7fd6f","tid":808674,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"日出康城附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da10e6d8bbd01941a4166c4deda208c9798e9ef","tid":808674,"uid":197959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f51cef43ef1835b835bc03d33e72b6c0172a0b0","tid":808674,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣已經係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:46:37.000Z","msg":"會嘈到人<br />\n唔係郊區一定會比人長期check住"},{"pid":"28ae933659fbc1ae64e717c3dd064a6bcad6b80b","tid":808674,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:49:57.000Z","msg":"喺食水中投毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232bf462310c7bbbd1775d2b558c7ea14bc62fc1","tid":808674,"uid":197959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"其實真係諗得過<br />\n又可以慳錢,又可以比更好嘅醫療比有需要嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67482776f24d31879b4ce4ec6fc3155c9c9dccb","tid":808674,"uid":206987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"黃大仙"},{"pid":"306b992b17d0f8ec2a6c3e08741cd7e827d9f0ea","tid":808674,"uid":197959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28ae933659fbc1ae64e717c3dd064a6bcad6b80b","tid":808674,"uid":46862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:49:57.000Z","msg":"喺食水中投毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"一定係你發夢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f226378791a1e82f7417d7b2afba9dd3388bbf","tid":808674,"uid":9825,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0